      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RED HOT BERNIE (2) has some solid form under his belt and proved too classy last time to win by 4 lengths at this track in a handy 15.84 beating CHEERS JAX. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from three starts. Expected to be right there at the finish again. MAD HOWLER (7) finished well back at Mandurah last time when a 9 length eighth (17.75) but scored three back at Mandurah (17.26). Was a winner at his only start from this draw. In the mix. SASSY SNICKERS (3) collided in the run but boxed on to place when a 0.8 lengths second in fast time (17.31) in a Free For All at Mandurah. Bold showing expected again. LIBERTY STAR (1) cannot be left out over a shorter trip.",
